# VitePress build output + cache
.vitepress/dist/
.vitepress/cache/

# Generated, but tracked: contributing/index.md, contributing/code-of-conduct.md,
# contributing/security.md, contributing/third-party-notices.md, and
# reference/changelog.md are kept under version control so a fresh clone has
# working dead-link resolution. The `predev` / `build` hook regenerates them
# from the canonical root files on every run.

# llms artefacts are generated on every build and should not be committed
public/llms.txt
public/llms-full.txt
